long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When you check the NATNEG of your Mario Kart Wii room on https://wiimmfi.de/stats/mkw you may find it difficult to understand the diagram, with its dots, triangles, and random letters that make absolutely no sense.

But worry no more! With this chrome extension, the confusing matrix is edited to display a beautiful picture of NUTMEG to aid your understanding!

As the great Feren OS Dev once said:
"Can someone check the NUTMEG of this room again to see if it's all fixed?"




If you're wondering why this plugin exists, watch the first two minutes of https://youtu.be/6Knhq0n07-Q

This plugin is not affiliated with the developers of Wiimmfi, KevinVG207, or The Feren OS Dev himself
